ActOther Than Statutory Authority
Indian Act
SubjectWhitefish River First Nation Boundaries Specific Claim Settlement ** Agreement **
PrecisOrder (1) authorizing the Minister of Crown-Indigenous Relations to ENTER INTO and EXECUTE, on behalf of Her Majesty in Right of Canada, the WHITEFISH RIVER FIRST NATION BOUNDARIES SPECIFIC CLAIM SETTLEMENT AGREEMENT; and (2) accepting the assent to release and relinquish absolutely to Canada all rights and interests in the lands as forming part of the Whitefish River Indian Reserve.
